This is a great collection of SIFI movies. My grand-daughter and I watched them together.
I had all these movies on VHS except for the return to the Return to the Lost World which was pretty good too.
Three pretty good dino movies in one package. Good deal.

I like the Lost World and Return to the Lost World, so I'm very happy with this set and the price.  BUT, if you want the full-length (250 minutes) version of Dinotopia, DON'T BUY THIS SET!!!!  They've chopped out so many little parts that I didn't even finish watching it. I probably won't even watch Journey to the Center of the Earth.  I only watch the Pat Boone and Brendan Frasier versions of that movie.
I like the first two movies, specially.
